---
title: Seared Greek-Style Shrimp with Lemon Potatoes and Yogurt-Feta Dip
description: Get ready to dig into spiced shrimp and lemony roasted potatoes with a zesty DIY yogurt-feta dip. Don't forget the tomato and spring mix chopped salad to round out this weeknight winner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/seared-greek-style-shrimp-6bcf1367.jpg
